nodes.text: Queb was an Ovissian male who served as the regent of the Galactic Republic-aligned planet Krystar. Queb was secretly working with the Confederacy of Independent Systems, holding numerous clone troopers prisoner and selling them to a Trandoshan hunter. Vishar Koss, a representative of Krystar, contacted Senator Padmé Amidala for assistance, and Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi undertook a mission to Krystar, rescuing the troopers and sending a team to take Queb into custody.
